headline: onsemi to Announce First Quarter Financial Results
summary: SCOTTSDALE, Ariz., April 17, 2025--onsemi (Nasdaq: ON) plans to announce its financial results for the first quarter, which ended April 4, 2025, before the market opens on Monday, May 5, 2025.
